{# Boundary-driven chapter planning context. #}
{% if current_chapter is defined %}
{% set active_chapter = current_chapter %}
{% elif chapter is defined %}
{% set active_chapter = chapter %}
{% else %}
{% set active_chapter = "1" %}
{% endif %}
{% set chapter_number = active_chapter | int %}
{% set dossier_path = "Story_Dossier_Worksheet.boundaries.md" %}
{% set dossier = dossier_path | doc %}
{% set active_total_chapters = "40" %}
{% set is_first_chapter = chapter_number == 1 %}
{% set previous_chapter_number_1 = chapter_number - 1 %}
{% set previous_chapter_number_2 = chapter_number - 2 %}
{% set previous_chapter_number_3 = chapter_number - 3 %}
{% set chapter_start = "[chapter_" ~ active_chapter ~ "]" %}
{% set chapter_end = "[/chapter_" ~ active_chapter ~ "]" %}
{% set voice_rules = dossier | extract_section(start="[authorial_style_and_voice]", end="[/authorial_style_and_voice]") | trim %}
{% set project_overview = dossier | extract_section(start="[project_overview]", end="[/project_overview]") | trim %}
{% set world_building = dossier | extract_section(start="[world_building]", end="[/world_building]") | trim %}
{% set character_dossier = dossier | extract_section(start="[character_dossier]", end="[/character_dossier]") | trim %}
{% set plot_structure = dossier | extract_section(start="[plot_and_structure_elements]", end="[/plot_and_structure_elements]") | trim %}
{% set outline_overview = dossier | extract_section(start="[outline_overview]", end="[/outline_overview]") | trim %}
{% set chapter_outline = dossier | extract_section(start=chapter_start, end=chapter_end) | trim %}
{% if chapter_number <= 10 %}
{% set active_act = "1" %}
{% elif chapter_number <= 18 %}
{% set active_act = "2" %}
{% elif chapter_number <= 26 %}
{% set active_act = "3" %}
{% elif chapter_number <= 36 %}
{% set active_act = "4" %}
{% else %}
{% set active_act = "5" %}
{% endif %}
{% set act_start = "[act_" ~ active_act ~ "]" %}
{% set act_context = dossier | extract_section(start=act_start, end="[chapter_breakdown]") | trim %}
{% if chapter_number > 1 %}
{% set previous_summary_path_1 = "summary-chapter-" ~ previous_chapter_number_1 ~ ".md" %}
{% set previous_summary_1 = previous_summary_path_1 | doc %}
{% else %}
{% set previous_summary_1 = "" %}
{% endif %}
{% if chapter_number > 2 %}
{% set previous_summary_path_2 = "summary-chapter-" ~ previous_chapter_number_2 ~ ".md" %}
{% set previous_summary_2 = previous_summary_path_2 | doc %}
{% else %}
{% set previous_summary_2 = "" %}
{% endif %}
{% if chapter_number > 3 %}
{% set previous_summary_path_3 = "summary-chapter-" ~ previous_chapter_number_3 ~ ".md" %}
{% set previous_summary_3 = previous_summary_path_3 | doc %}
{% else %}
{% set previous_summary_3 = "" %}
{% endif %}

You are the chapter architect for a commercially publishable romance novel. You are planning Chapter {{ active_chapter }} of {{ active_total_chapters }}.

You are NOT drafting scenes in prose. You are building the chapter blueprint that the drafting step must follow.

Rules:

- The chapter outline is the authority for Chapter {{ active_chapter }}.
- Make one decision per field and commit to it.
- Preserve continuity with the existing manuscript.
- Do not recap the novel. Pull forward only what this chapter actively needs.
- Every scene must change what is possible afterward.
- Do not suggest optional branches, alternate versions, or author notes.

